text: Go Yoon-hwan (; born August 26, 1998), better known by his stage name Ryeoun (), is a South Korean actor. He is best known for his roles in 18 Again (2020), The World of My 17 (2020) and Adult Trainee (2021). == References == == Other websites == * * Ryeoun at Lucky Company Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean actors
